author: kkolinko
msg: Various improvements to the Windows installer to be able to install several copies of Tomcat 6 side by side. Allow to configure service name, connector and shutdown ports. Allow to choose whether to install Start menu shortcuts and Apache Tomcat monitor application for all users or for the current one only. Improve server.xml file handling. Fix uninstallation icon.
